oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Benefit Ball featuring Grand Ole Opry stars at Sid's Roller Rink
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dances; Grand ole opry (Radio program);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (red on white) announcing a Big Benefit Ball featuring stars of the Grand Ole Opry including Jackie Phelps, Johnny Johnson, Pete Drake, Marshall Barnes, Jack Little and others at Sid's Roller Rink on October 31.
